Cellphone video captures the moment a 23-year-old woman was rescued from underneath the ruins of a collapsed minimart two days after a magnitude 7.0 earthquake struck Indonesia's resort island of Lombok.

The woman is reportedly recovering in the hospital. https://t.co/TppD0vUE6W https://t.co/luPT06QKhE
